        <div class="success-box">
            <h3>✅ Widget Demo Page</h3>
            <p>This page demonstrates the IntalksAI Call Control Ribbon widget.</p>
            <p><strong>Widget URL:</strong> <a href="http://intalksai-call-ribbon-widget-844605843483.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com">http://intalksai-call-ribbon-widget-844605843483.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>API URL:</strong> <a href="http://production.eba-tpbtmere.us-east-1.elasticbeanstalk.com">http://production.eba-tpbtmere.us-east-1.elasticbeanstalk.com</a></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>📋 How to Test:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Wait for initialization</strong> - The ribbon will load automatically</li>
                <li><strong>Click on a customer card</strong> above to load their phone number</li>
                <li><strong>Look at the bottom of the page</strong> - You'll see the IntalksAI Call Ribbon</li>
